  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>Open <em>DropDown </em>for 'Custom TreeView ComboBox' <em>ComboBox </em>and <em>DropDown </em>will be opened with text and images.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>&nbsp;The example contains&nbsp;the demonstrated <em>ComboBox</em>, which&nbsp;has <em>DataSource </em>as the array of objects that have public property 'Photo' with <em>ResourceHandle </em>type. And the 'Photo' property is set as <em>ImageMember </em>for the <em>ComboBox</em>.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
